# Per-module resource utilization report.
# Runs synth_ecp5 with -noflatten so stat prints per-module breakdown.
# Invoked AFTER read_verilog (file list passed by Makefile).

# -run begin:check skips the internal stat that synth_ecp5 runs
# during its check stage, avoiding duplicate output.
synth_ecp5 -noflatten -nowidelut -top gpu_top -run begin:check
stat
